The form of the conserved current can be derived systematically by applying Noether&#x27;s theorem to the formula_56 symmetry. We will not do so here, but simply verify that this current is conserved.

From the Klein–Gordon equation for a complex field formula_63 of mass formula_64, written in covariant notation and &quot;mostly plus&quot; signature,
