Applying this to the derivative of the current formula_74 one finds
:formula_61

This formula_56 symmetry is a global symmetry, but it can also be gauged to create a local or gauge symmetry: see below scalar QED. The name of gauge symmetry is somewhat misleading: it is really a redundancy, while the global symmetry is a genuine symmetry.

== Lagrangian formulation ==
The Klein–Gordon equation can also be derived by a variational method, arising as the Euler–Lagrange equation of the action

